                                                    <TextBlock x:Name="ClosedCaptionSettingText" 
                                                               x:Uid="ClosedCaptionSetting" 
                                                               Text="[자막 설정]"
                                                               VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                               Margin="12,0"/>
                                                </StackPanel>
                                            </ListViewItem>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                    </Flyout>
                                </AppBarButton.Flyout>
                            </AppBarButton>
                        </Grid>
                        <AppBarButton x:Name="FastRewindButton" 
                                      x:Uid="FastRewind" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[뒤로 감기]"
                                      Width="{Binding Width, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      Height="{Binding Height, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      VerticalAlignment='Center'>
                            <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                <FontIcon Glyph="&#xEB9E;" Margin="{Binding Margin, ElementName=AppBarIconFrame}"/>
                            </AppBarButton.Icon>
                        </AppBarButton>
                        <AppBarButton x:Name="PlayPauseButton" 
                                      x:Uid="PlayPause"
                                      ToolTipService.ToolTip="{Binding Tag, ElementName=PlayPauseButton, FallbackValue='[재생/정지]'}"
                                      Width="{Binding Width, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      Height="{Binding Height, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      VerticalAlignment='Center'>
                            <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                <SymbolIcon x:Uid='PlayPause2' x:Name='PlayPauseSymbol' Symbol='Play' Margin="{Binding Margin, ElementName=AppBarIconFrame}" />
                            </AppBarButton.Icon>
                        </AppBarButton>
                        <AppBarButton x:Name="FastForwardButton" 
                                      x:Uid="FastForward" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[빨리 감기]"
                                      Width="{Binding Width, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      Height="{Binding Height, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      VerticalAlignment='Center'>
                            <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                <FontIcon Glyph="&#xEB9D;" Margin="{Binding Margin, ElementName=AppBarIconFrame}"/>
                            </AppBarButton.Icon>
                        </AppBarButton>
                        <AppBarButton x:Name='FullWindowButton'
                                      x:Uid="FullWindow"
                                      ToolTipService.ToolTip="{Binding Tag, ElementName=FullWindowButton, FallbackValue='[전체 화면]'}"
                                      Width="{Binding Width, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      Height="{Binding Height, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      VerticalAlignment='Center'
                                      Visibility="Collapsed">
                            <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                <SymbolIcon x:Uid="FullWindow2" x:Name='FullWindowSymbol' Symbol='FullScreen' Margin="{Binding Margin, ElementName=AppBarIconFrame}" />
                            </AppBarButton.Icon>
                        </AppBarButton>
                        <Grid>
                            <Rectangle x:Name="AudioMoreIndicator"
                                       Visibility="Collapsed"
                                       Style="{StaticResource MoreRectangleStyle}"/>
                            <AppBarButton x:Name="AudioButton" 
                                          x:Uid="Audio" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[오디오]"
                                          Width="{Binding Width, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                          Height="{Binding Height, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                          DataContext="{Binding CCPMediaElement, ElementName=CCPMediaTransportControls}"
                                          VerticalAlignment='Center'>
                                <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                    <SymbolIcon x:Name="AudioMuteSymbol" Symbol="Volume" Margin="{Binding Margin, ElementName=AppBarIconFrame}" />
                                </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                <AppBarButton.Flyout>
                                    <Flyout FlyoutPresenterStyle="{StaticResource FlyoutStyle}">
                                        <StackPanel Margin="6">
                                            <StackPanel x:Name="AudioVolumeBoosterItem" Visibility="Collapsed" 
                                                        x:Uid="AudioVolumeBooster" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[음량 부스터]" 
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton x:Name="AudioVolumeBoosterButton"
                                                              Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                              Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}"
                                                              RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5">
                                                    <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                        <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE789;" Margin="8,0" />
                                                    </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                </AppBarButton>
                                                <Slider x:Name="AudioVolumeBoosterSlider" 
                                                        Minimum="0"
                                                        Value="{Binding VolumeBoost, FallbackValue=0, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                        Maximum="60"
                                                        StepFrequency="1"
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutSliderStyle}"/>
                                                <Grid Width="65">
                                                    <TextBlock VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                                               Margin="12,0,6,0">
                                                        <Run Text="{Binding Value, ElementName=AudioVolumeBoosterSlider}" />
                                                        <Run Text="dB"/>
                                                    </TextBlock>
                                                </Grid>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                            <StackPanel x:Name="AudioSyncItem" Visibility="Collapsed" 
                                                        x:Uid="AudioSync" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[오디오 싱크]" 
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton x:Name="AudioSyncButton"
                                                              Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                              Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}"
                                                              RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5">
                                                    <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                        <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE81C;" Margin="8,0" />
                                                    </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                </AppBarButton>
                                                <Slider x:Name="AudioSyncSlider" 
                                                        Minimum="-3"
                                                        Value="{Binding AudioSync, FallbackValue=0, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                        Maximum="0"
                                                        StepFrequency="0.2"
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutSliderStyle}" />
                                                <Grid Width="65">
                                                    <TextBlock VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                                               Margin="12,0,6,0">
                                                        <Run Text="{Binding Value, ElementName=AudioSyncSlider}" />
                                                        <Run x:Uid="SecondUnit" Text="[sec]" />
                                                    </TextBlock>
                                                </Grid>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                            <StackPanel x:Name="AudioLanguagesItem" Visibility="Collapsed" 
                                                        x:Uid="AudioLanguage" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[오디오 언어]" 
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                                <SymbolIcon Symbol="Character" Margin="8,0" />
                                                <ComboBox x:Name="AudioLanguagesComboBox" 
                                                          ItemsSource="{x:Bind AudioStreamLanguageSource}"
                                                          SelectedIndex="{Binding AudioStreamLanguageIndex, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                          VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                          BorderThickness="0"
                                                          Background="Transparent"
                                                          SelectedValuePath="Key"
                                                          DisplayMemberPath="Name" />
                                            </StackPanel>
                                            <StackPanel x:Uid="AudioBalance" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[좌우 균형]" 
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton x:Name="AudioBalanceButton"
                                                          Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                          Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}">
                                                    <AppBarButton.Content>
                                                        <Grid Width="48">
                                                            <SymbolIcon Symbol="Volume" RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5" >
                                                                <SymbolIcon.RenderTransform>
                                                                    <CompositeTransform ScaleX="0.7" ScaleY="0.7" TranslateX="-3" TranslateY="-6" Rotation="180" />
                                                                </SymbolIcon.RenderTransform>
                                                            </SymbolIcon>
                                                            <SymbolIcon Symbol="Volume" RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5" >
                                                                <SymbolIcon.RenderTransform>
                                                                    <CompositeTransform ScaleX="0.7" ScaleY="0.7" TranslateX="3" TranslateY="6" />
                                                                </SymbolIcon.RenderTransform>
                                                            </SymbolIcon>
                                                        </Grid>
                                                    </AppBarButton.Content>
                                                </AppBarButton>
                                                
                                                <Slider x:Name="BalanceSlider" 
                                                        Minimum="-100"
                                                        Value="{Binding Balance, FallbackValue=0, Mode=TwoWay, Converter={StaticResource PercentageFormatter}}"
                                                        Maximum="100"
                                                        StepFrequency="1"
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutSliderStyle}"/>
                                                <Grid Width="65">
                                                    <TextBlock VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                                               Margin="12,0,6,0">
                                                        <Run Text="{Binding Value, ElementName=BalanceSlider}" />
                                                        <Run x:Uid="PercentageUnit" />
                                                    </TextBlock>
                                                </Grid>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                            <StackPanel x:Uid="AudioVolume" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[음량]" 
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton x:Name="VolumeMuteButton"
                                                              Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                              Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}"
                                                              RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5">
                                                    <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                        <SymbolIcon x:Name="VolumeMuteSymbol" Symbol="Volume" />
                                                    </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                </AppBarButton>
                                                <Slider x:Name="VolumeSlider" 
                                                        Minimum="0"
                                                        Value="{Binding Volume, FallbackValue=100, Mode=TwoWay, Converter={StaticResource PercentageFormatter}}"
                                                        Maximum="100"
                                                        StepFrequency="1"
                                                        Style="{StaticResource FlyoutSliderStyle}" />
                                                <Grid Width="65">
                                                    <TextBlock VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                                               Margin="12,0,6,0">
                                                        <Run Text="{Binding Value, ElementName=VolumeSlider}" />
                                                        <Run x:Uid="PercentageUnit" />
                                                    </TextBlock>
                                                </Grid>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                    </Flyout>
                                </AppBarButton.Flyout>
                            </AppBarButton>
                        </Grid>
                        <AppBarButton x:Name="DisplayButton" 
                                      x:Uid="Video" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[비디오 옵션]" 
                                      Width="{Binding Width, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      Height="{Binding Height, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      DataContext="{Binding ElementName=CCPMediaTransportControls}"
                                      VerticalAlignment='Center'>
                            <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE714;" Margin="{Binding Margin, ElementName=AppBarIconFrame}"/>
                            </AppBarButton.Icon>
                            <AppBarButton.Flyout>
                                <Flyout FlyoutPresenterStyle="{StaticResource FlyoutStyle}" >
                                    <StackPanel Margin="6">
                                        <ListViewItem x:Name="RotationLockItem" Padding="0" Visibility="Collapsed"
                                                      ToolTipService.ToolTip="{Binding Label, ElementName=RotationLockButton, FallbackValue='[회전 잠금]'}">
                                            <AppBarToggleButton x:Name="RotationLockButton" 
                                                                x:Uid="RotationLock"
                                                                Label="[회전 잠금]"
                                                                IsThreeState="False"
                                                                IsChecked="{Binding CCPMediaElement.EnabledRotationLock, FallbackValue=True, Mode=TwoWay, Converter={StaticResource BoolToNullableBoolConverter}}"
                                                                Style="{StaticResource FlyoutAppBarToggleButtonStyle}"
                                                                Width="{Binding ActualWidth, ElementName=RotationLockItem}">
                                                <AppBarToggleButton.Icon>
                                                    <FontIcon x:Name="RotationLockIcon" Glyph="&#xE755;" Margin="8,0" />
                                                </AppBarToggleButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarToggleButton>
                                        </ListViewItem>
                                        <StackPanel x:Uid="AspectRatio" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[화면 비율]"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}" >
                                            <AppBarButton x:Name="AspectRatioButton"
                                                          Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                          Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                    <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE799;" />
                                                </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarButton>
                                            <ComboBox x:Name="AspectRatioComboBox"
                                                      ItemsSource="{x:Bind AspectRatioSource}"
                                                      SelectedIndex="{Binding AspectRatioIndex, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                      VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                      BorderThickness="0"
                                                      Background="Transparent"
                                                      SelectedValuePath="Key"
                                                      DisplayMemberPath="Name"/>                                           
                                        </StackPanel>
                                        <ListViewItem x:Name="HorizontalMirrorItem" Padding="0"  Visibility="Collapsed"
                                                      ToolTipService.ToolTip="{Binding Label, ElementName=HorizontalMirrorButton, FallbackValue='[좌우 반전]'}">
                                            <AppBarToggleButton x:Name="HorizontalMirrorButton" 
                                                                x:Uid="HorizontalMirror" 
                                                                Label="[좌우 반전]"
                                                                IsThreeState="False"
                                                                IsChecked="{Binding CCPMediaElement.EnabledHorizontalMirror, FallbackValue=True, Mode=TwoWay, Converter={StaticResource BoolToNullableBoolConverter}}"
                                                                Style="{StaticResource FlyoutAppBarToggleButtonStyle}"
                                                                Width="{Binding ActualWidth, ElementName=HorizontalMirrorItem}">
                                                <AppBarToggleButton.Icon>
                                                    <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE11E;" Margin="8,0" />
                                                </AppBarToggleButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarToggleButton>
                                        </ListViewItem>
                                        <StackPanel x:Name="DisplayRotationItem" Visibility="Collapsed" 
                                                    x:Uid="DisplayRotation" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[화면 회전]"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                            <AppBarButton x:Name="DisplayRotationButton"
                                                          Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                          Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                    <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE14F;" RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5">
                                                        <FontIcon.RenderTransform>
                                                            <CompositeTransform ScaleX="-1"/>
                                                        </FontIcon.RenderTransform>
                                                    </FontIcon>
                                                </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarButton>
                                            <ComboBox x:Name="DisplayRotationComboBox"
                                                      ItemsSource="{x:Bind DisplayRotationSource}"
                                                      SelectedIndex="{Binding DisplayRotationIndex, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                      VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                      BorderThickness="0"
                                                      Background="Transparent"
                                                      SelectedValuePath="Key"
                                                      DisplayMemberPath="Name"/>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                        <StackPanel x:Name="DisplayZoomPanel"
                                                    x:Uid="DisplayZoomItem" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[확대 및 축소]"
                                                    Visibility="Collapsed"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}" >
                                            <AppBarButton x:Name="DisplayZoomButton"
                                                          Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                          Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                    <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE8A3;" />
                                                </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarButton>
                                            <Slider x:Name="DisplayZoomSlider" 
                                                    Minimum="0.5"
                                                    Value="{Binding CCPMediaElement.ZoomInOut, FallbackValue=1, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                    Maximum="4"
                                                    StepFrequency="0.1"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutSliderStyle}" />
                                            <Grid Width="65">
                                                <TextBlock VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                           HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                                           Margin="12,0,6,0">
                                                <Run Text="{Binding Value, ElementName=DisplayZoomSlider, FallbackValue=1, Converter={StaticResource ZoomValueFormatter}}" />
                                                <Run Text="X" />
                                                </TextBlock>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                        <StackPanel x:Uid="PlaybackRepeat" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[반복 재생]"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                            <AppBarButton x:Name="PlaybackRepeatButton"
                                                          Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                          Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                    <SymbolIcon Symbol="RepeatAll" />
                                                </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarButton>
                                            <!--<SymbolIcon Margin="8,0" Symbol="RepeatAll" />-->
                                            <ComboBox x:Name="PlaybackRepeatComboBox"
                                                      ItemsSource="{x:Bind PlaybackRepeatSource}"
                                                      SelectedIndex="{Binding PlaybackRepeatIndex, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                      VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                      BorderThickness="0"
                                                      Background="Transparent"
                                                      SelectedValuePath="Key"
                                                      DisplayMemberPath="Name"/>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                        <StackPanel x:Uid="Brightness" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[화면 밝기]"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                            <AppBarButton x:Name="BrightnessButton"
                                                          Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                          Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                    <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE706;" />
                                                </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarButton>
                                            <Slider x:Name="BrightnessSlider"
                                                    Minimum="20"
                                                    Value="{Binding CCPMediaElement.Brightness, FallbackValue=100, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                    Maximum="100"
                                                    StepFrequency="1"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutSliderStyle}" />
                                            <Grid Width="65">
                                                <TextBlock VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                           HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                                           Margin="12,0,6,0">
                                                    <Run Text="{Binding Value, ElementName=BrightnessSlider}" />
                                                    <Run x:Uid="PercentageUnit" />
                                                </TextBlock>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                        <StackPanel x:Uid="PlaybackRate" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[재생 속도]"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}" >
                                            <AppBarButton x:Name="PlaybackRateButton"
                                                          Margin="-6,0,0,0"
                                                          Style="{StaticResource AppBarButtonStyle}">
                                                <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                                    <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE1D5;" />
                                                </AppBarButton.Icon>
                                            </AppBarButton>
                                            <Slider x:Name="PlaybackRateSlider" 
                                                    Minimum="0.5"
                                                    Value="{Binding PlaybackRate, FallbackValue=1, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                                    Maximum="4"
                                                    StepFrequency="0.1"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutSliderStyle}" />
                                            <Grid Width="65">
                                                <TextBlock VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                                           HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                                           Margin="12,0,6,0">
                                                    <Run Text="{Binding Value, ElementName=PlaybackRateSlider}" />
                                                    <Run Text="X" />
                                                </TextBlock>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                        <StackPanel x:Uid="Decoder" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[비디오 디코더]"
                                                    Style="{StaticResource FlyoutMenuItemStyle}">
                                            <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE950;" Margin="8,0" />
                                            <RadioButton x:Name="HWDecoderButton"
                                                         GroupName="Decoder" MinWidth="66" Margin="14,0,0,0">HW</RadioButton>
                                            <RadioButton x:Name="HybridDecoderButton" 
                                                         GroupName="Decoder" MinWidth="96" Margin="12,0,0,0">Hybrid</RadioButton>
                                            <RadioButton x:Name="SWDecoderButton" 
                                                         GroupName="Decoder" MinWidth="48" Margin="12,0,0,0">SW</RadioButton>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                    </StackPanel>
                                </Flyout>
                            </AppBarButton.Flyout>
                        </AppBarButton>
                        <AppBarButton x:Name="LockControlPanelButton"
                                      x:Uid="LockControlPanel" ToolTipService.ToolTip="[재생패널 잠금]"
                                      Width="{Binding Width, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      Height="{Binding Height, ElementName=AppBarButtonFrame}"
                                      VerticalAlignment='Center'>
                            <AppBarButton.Icon>
                                <FontIcon Glyph="&#xE1F6;" Margin="{Binding Margin, ElementName=AppBarIconFrame}" />
                            </AppBarButton.Icon>
                        </AppBarButton>
                    </StackPanel>
                </Border>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</UserControl>
